import styled from "styled-components"
import Announcment from "../components/Announcment"
import Footer from "../components/Footer"
import Navbar from "../components/navbar"
import Newsletter from "../components/Newsletter"

const Container = styled.div``

export default function ProductPage() {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Announcment/>
        <Navbar/>
        <Wrapper>
            <ImgContainer>
                <Image src= "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/3099/8088/products/bento_1512x.jpg?v=1649695087" />
            </ImgContainer>
            <InfoContainer>
                <Title>GMK BENTO R2</Title>
                <Desc>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Iure voluptatem doloribus consectetur tempore sint expedita eveniet! Eos asperiores quisquam, dolore voluptate sit accusantium nostrum adipisci voluptates architecto odit pariatur deleniti!</Desc>
                <Price>$500</Price>
            </InfoContainer>
        </Wrapper>
        <Newsletter/>
        <Footer/>
    </Container>
  )
}
